			<div class="col-md-11 col-sm-11 col-xs-12 no-padding">
				<h1>Adobe warns of Flash zero&#8209;day vulnerability, being actively exploited by online criminals</h1>
<div class="excerpt">Adobe Flash users find themselves in danger once again, as they wait for an emergency security patch to fix a vulnerability being actively exploited in the wild.</div>
<div class="post-meta">
    <div class="wls-authors">
